\newlabel{fig:attn}{{6}{8}{Hop-by-hop attention heatmaps for a Task~16 test example. Left: unsupervised model (attention is diffuse). Right: semi-supervised model with 50\% labeled training examples (attention is sharply concentrated on the induction rule sentence at hop 1). Supporting fact sentences are highlighted in green}{figure.6}{}}
